Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,------------------text-----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.93,0:00:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.41,0:00:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,今天真早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.90,0:00:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不知怎麼的就醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.09,0:00:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子他媽 你看看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.21,0:00:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,誒? 這不是我們新婚那次嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.84,0:00:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我整理抽屜的時候發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.43,0:00:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好年輕! 話說那時我真是可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.41,0:00:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,親愛的 你現在也很可愛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.72,0:00:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.69,0:00:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,和小愛結婚 我每天都像是做夢一樣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.20,0:00:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,修吾你真會說話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.06,0:00:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.93,0:00:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,修吾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.79,0:00:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.81,0:00:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,修吾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.72,0:00:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.32,0:00:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.34,0:00:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 你剛才…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.25,0:00:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我要遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.45,0:00:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.81,0:00:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.74,0:00:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,社團那邊你已經引退了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.06,0:01:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,今天早上有畢業相冊製作委員會議
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.59,0:01:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.10,0:01:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.40,0:01:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 未乃愛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.85,0:01:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你們剛才看到姐姐的臉…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.91,0:01:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.19,0:01:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,討厭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.19,0:01:33.35,comment,,0,0,0,,註:「ゆいっちんぐ」->「まいっちんぐ」,出自「まいっちんぐマチコ先生」:「討厭啦!真知子老師」,\N原作漫畫最早於1980年開始連載。
Comment: 0,0:01:47.37,0:01:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,「動畫沉寂會」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.19,0:03:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,臉很奇怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 雖然很快又變回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.02,0:03:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪是怎麼個奇怪法?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼奇怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.21,0:03:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 就像以前的動畫人物一樣臉變扁了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.16,0:03:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,看來未乃愛你是太疲憊了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.48,0:03:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟學園祭之後發生了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.16,0:03:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我啊 我說的是真…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.91,0:03:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.43,0:03:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,小…小唯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.02,0:03:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.34,0:03:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.18,0:03:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我說那兩個人的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.67,0:03:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你很沒禮貌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.46,0:03:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,哪裡奇怪了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.44,0:03:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你問哪裡? 看了還不明白嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.18,0:03:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.06,0:03:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,第一節是美術課哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.84,0:03:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多該換教室了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:03:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好了好了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.53,0:03:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼 這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.50,0:04:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.41,0:04:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.87,0:04:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.15,0:04:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,剛剛這邊是有什麼東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.37,0:04:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好像有什麼黑暗的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.96,0:04:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,漆黑而幽暗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,吞噬一切的地獄…地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,就像那地獄一般啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,振作一點啊 未乃愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡什麼都沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.08,0:04:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,之前是有的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.40,0:04:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我一走到這邊…
Comment: 0,0:04:30.28,0:04:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,誒?誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.52,0:04:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是吃了什麼奇怪的東西?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,未乃愛正看到一些我們看不見的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要去保健室?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.18,0:04:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,誒? 剛才就在這的啊
Comment: 0,0:04:45.74,0:04:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.53,0:05:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.34,0:05:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,未乃愛 午飯你打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.35,0:05:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,便當? 還是去買麵包?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.42,0:05:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,今天的午間套餐B有炸雞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.40,0:05:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那還真是讓人難以割捨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.41,0:05:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,未乃愛 午休的時候有部會哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.16,0:05:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.76,0:05:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,課一下子就上完了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.26,0:05:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,這不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.68,0:05:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,從第一節課開始到現在也就過了一分多鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.82,0:05:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你還是喝點東西冷靜一下吧 未乃愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.68,0:05:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,塞巴斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,女僕?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.88,0:05:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,要那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.94,0:05:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,就交給塞巴斯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.36,0:05:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,她說話了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,請享用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\fe0}S'il vous plaît
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,塞巴斯 做得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.16,0:06:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你的動作很精彩呢 塞巴斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要加入田徑部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.90,0:06:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.71,0:06:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.27,0:06:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這個能給我一個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.46,0:06:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.25,0:06:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那老師我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.55,0:06:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,眼睛閃閃發光!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你們要了什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,未乃愛 你說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.10,0:06:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,確實不太對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.42,0:06:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你終於發現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.07,0:06:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,以往這時塞巴斯都會沏一杯格雷伯爵茶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.96,0:06:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,而這卻是焙茶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.09,0:06:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.98,0:06:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是那裡不對勁嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.06,0:06:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,關於明年部長的人選…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.45,0:06:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,大家不覺得奇怪嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.98,0:06:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,哪有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.77,0:06:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,所有社團都開始討論換屆的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.50,0:06:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是說這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,周圍的一切都在變得不正常吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.04,0:06:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,周圍?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.19,0:06:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,未乃愛一大早開始就是這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.38,0:07:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪? 你覺得什麼奇怪了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.13,0:07:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你那邊就很奇怪!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.42,0:07:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,未乃愛是不是看到了些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.21,0:07:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那你也終於擁有了邪眼的力…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.54,0:07:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,才沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.80,0:07:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,周圍一切都很奇怪 你們注意不到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.40,0:07:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,或許有點奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.49,0:07:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你這麼說是有點感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,或許是動畫的總編劇換人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.89,0:07:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,總編劇?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能 都已經這麼多集了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.06,0:07:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是田廣溜了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.06,0:07:28.53,comment,,0,0,0,,註:「田広」->「広田光毅」:「廣田光毅」,該作的總編劇。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,只不過是那個傢伙被替換了 會有這麼大影響嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.83,0:07:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼?什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.98,0:07:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你們在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.40,0:07:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,看來需要確認一下情況啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.77,0:07:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們再看一遍片頭曲?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.62,0:07:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,片頭曲?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.00,0:07:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,再看一次?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.30,0:07:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我倒帶了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.63,0:07:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,討厭啦
Comment: 0,0:08:12.88,0:08:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,「動畫沉寂會」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.22,0:08:25.96,op - jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}何をしてても退屈な every day
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.75,0:08:27.17,op - jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}コ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.22,0:08:25.96,op - cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不管做什麼 每天都是那麼無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.75,0:08:27.17,op - cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}一…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.24,0:08:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是沒什麼變化嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.02,0:08:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,誒?不是不是 剛才那是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼大家都這麼平靜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.27,0:08:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你冷靜點 未乃愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.36,0:08:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,都這個階段了要是我們太動搖 會被11集棄番的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.23,0:08:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,11集棄番?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.56,0:08:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,因為和至今為止看到的劇情發展不太一樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.98,0:08:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,觀眾可能會說我們題材不明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.61,0:08:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我們定位為什麼題材 觀眾才會認可呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,日常?校園?萌?少女?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.99,0:08:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟動畫題材近年來被細分得越來越複雜了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.12,0:09:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,至少我們要先確定一下是搞笑動漫還是現實動漫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.24,0:09:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那接下來就需要爆炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.03,0:09:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,爆炸?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,閃光及衝擊波防護措施!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:08.59,comment,,0,0,0,,註:「対閃光、対ショック防御」->「対ショック、 対閃光防御」,「宇宙戰艦大和號」中波動炮發射準備環節的一環。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣子的是搞笑動漫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.94,0:09:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,眼…我的眼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.94,0:09:20.66,comment,,0,0,0,,註:「目が、目がぁ～!」,「天空之城」中最後階段希達與巴斯唸出咒語「巴魯斯!」,\N放出強光致使羅穆斯卡大佐短暫失明,大佐喊出的台詞。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.43,0:09:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是現實動漫的話就會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.97,0:09:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…但是我們卻還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,這完全不夠現實
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.01,0:09:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,要是現實的話會變成什麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.85,0:09:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,還能行!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.30,0:09:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,記得請我吃醋漬青花魚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.12,0:09:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,貓前輩!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.01,0:09:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,這很現實
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.05,0:09:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,確實現實
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.38,0:09:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,所謂現實…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.76,0:10:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,貓前輩!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.36,0:10:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,貓前輩!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正艺黑_GBK\fs70\bord0\b1\frz10.74\pos(602,675)}一同討論、\N盟友光輝背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.18,0:10:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.32,0:10:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.84,0:10:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我還以為我要死了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,未乃愛還不回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.44,0:10:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我想和貓前輩再聊會天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.71,0:10:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你今天反應有點劇烈很奇怪 我有點擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.17,0:10:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,大家反而覺得我是不正常的了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.19,0:10:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.44,0:10:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,光輝前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.72,0:10:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,光輝前輩?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.12,0:10:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,中野前輩!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.30,0:10:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:10:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.25,0:11:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩曾說過你們家是兄弟六人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,誒…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.87,0:11:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,最年長的哥哥年紀和你差很遠嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.95,0:11:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,比如差個20歲什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.12,0:11:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.92,0:11:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼這麼問?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.07,0:11:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事 這樣就沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.75,0:11:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.89,0:11:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你也辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.68,0:11:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙的兄弟們怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.60,0:11:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.83,0:11:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.43,0:11:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.29,0:11:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才好像是下了陣雨 你沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.71,0:12:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,回來得有點晚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.18,0:12:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 「天然女僕」的錄像我們已經看完了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.18,0:12:04.24,comment,,0,0,0,,註:「天然メイド」->「少年メイド」:「少年女僕」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.26,0:12:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,小未?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.04,0:12:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我…我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.74,0:12:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.72,0:12:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.98,0:12:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,這孩子怎麼了 突然這麼奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.98,0:12:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我們也已經看完「魔法使茉莉」了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.98,0:12:21.61,comment,,0,0,0,,註:「魔法使いモリー」->「魔法使いサリー」:「魔法使莎莉」,接下來的作畫神似魔法使莎莉。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.53,0:12:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.83,0:12:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,去準備晚飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.42,0:12:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.64,0:12:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那我也來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.11,0:12:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,來看看誰先跑到廚房
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.87,0:12:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,看起來好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.39,0:12:43.94,Default-up,,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.94,0:12:44.81,Default-up,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.15,0:13:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,痛!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.92,0:13:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.79,0:13:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,據說城市裡出現了巨型機械獸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.16,0:13:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,巨型機械獸?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.07,0:13:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,貌似正在朝這邊走來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,大家冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.61,0:13:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,結界已經佈置好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事 塊塊前輩倒是跟平時沒什麼不同
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.67,0:13:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,武藏鏡 塊!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.26,0:13:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,紅蓮射門!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:13:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,火力有點太猛了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼大家都絲毫不感到奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.56,0:14:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,這太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.79,0:14:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,這又不是動畫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.66,0:14:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,「又不是動畫」?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.00,0:14:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,這有什麼不好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.67,0:14:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,未乃愛從昨天開始就淨說些奇怪的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.17,0:14:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你的靈魂到底被什麼東西支配了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.52,0:14:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.04,0:14:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,動畫就是動畫 不是現實
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.48,0:14:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你們這才叫異常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.39,0:14:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你在否定動畫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.61,0:14:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,可怕的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.61,0:14:34.07,comment,,0,0,0,,註:梗「玻璃假面」中月影千草的台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.22,0:14:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,本以為你比任何人都要深愛著動畫研究部…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.03,0:14:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,結果…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.29,0:14:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,等下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.78,0:14:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,可怕的孩子!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.32,0:14:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,小有棲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.00,0:14:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不能接受動畫的方方面面 何談愛著動畫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.40,0:14:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你的交情到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.26,0:14:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,真是遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.12,0:14:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.86,0:15:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼突然就到傍晚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.53,0:15:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你的交情到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.48,0:15:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你在否定動畫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.12,0:15:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼…不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.11,0:15:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.15,0:15:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.46,0:15:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,小未 你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.39,0:16:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我很奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.44,0:16:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我不正常嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.44,0:16:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 是我出問題了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.08,0:16:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,小未…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.51,0:16:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.58,0:16:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,只要再忍耐一下就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.09,0:16:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,因為很快就要迎來結尾了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.45,0:16:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.60,0:16:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.89,0:16:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.88,0:16:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事 感覺我在被大家盯著看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.44,0:16:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,這有什麼辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.18,0:17:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說你說了討厭動畫是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.37,0:17:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這種話…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我才沒說過!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.83,0:17:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.84,0:17:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.15,0:17:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,光輝前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,能不要這樣叫我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.18,0:17:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,確實 有些東西不太對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.17,0:17:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.64,0:18:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不是未乃愛提醒 我可能也注意不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.22,0:18:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.87,0:18:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我都開始以為是自己不正常了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.64,0:18:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,應該是有什麼原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.87,0:18:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,原因?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.35,0:18:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,正常來講不該有的事開始發生一定是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.25,0:18:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你有什麼頭緒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.32,0:18:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,正常來講不該有的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.42,0:18:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,全都是因為你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.09,0:18:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,啥?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.95,0:18:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,早就覺得奇怪了 貓竟然會說話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.86,0:18:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你到現在才吐槽這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.24,0:18:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我第一次開門的時候 你出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.29,0:18:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那時還真是多謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.16,0:18:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,然後你就叫我別再打開那扇門了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.05,0:18:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,中野前輩和其他人在跟你交談後 事情就越變越怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.66,0:18:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,全都是因為你!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.58,0:18:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.59,0:19:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧 把一切弄清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,等…等等!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.66,0:19:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,門…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,全是我的回合!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:32.16,comment,,0,0,0,,//註:「すべて俺のターン」->「ずっと俺のターン」:一直是我的回合,用來揶揄對方;一說該梗出自「遊戲王」,\N而實際上其出處不明。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.21,0:19:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,出來吧!黑紅藍黃金色巨龍!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.58,0:19:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,召喚!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.04,0:19:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,小有棲 小美子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.42,0:19:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.92,0:20:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,連我也…變成動畫了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.96,0:20:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,枷鎖被解開了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.91,0:20:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.39,0:20:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,「觀察者」不在的現在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.85,0:20:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,平衡已經被打破了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.40,0:20:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.91,0:20:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.06,0:20:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你來自那邊嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 我是來自動畫世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.30,0:20:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.34,0:20:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,貓前輩是動畫?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,誒?竟然先吐槽我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.14,0:20:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,這個世界再過不久就要被動畫吞噬了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.15,0:20:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,吞噬?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.89,0:20:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你是誰派來的?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,如你所見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.52,0:21:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,新世界大爆炸!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.91,0:21:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,大家…
